      "content": "therapy won't fix the fact that my life's purpose was a delusion. it's like living a lie for a decade and a half. the exhaustion is just... it's too much. i look at the empty lab and i don't see a future, i just see the void where my life used to be. i'm just tired of pretending there's an \"after\" to this.",
